des:
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.
After connecting Alexa to your Euhomy products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our " Euhomy" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one tuya account in our " Euhomy" app;
(3). You need to have some Euhomy devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our " Euhomy" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Euhomy Smart" skill;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Euhomy Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Euhomy Smart", and you'll be navigated to Euhomy Smart login page;
(9). Input your Euhomy account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
